                  "pageId": 1581002,
                  "revisionId": 2742091,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "As noted above, the buff activates if the companion possesses over 1200 maximum shields through modding, and will remain active regardless of their actual moment-to-moment shield strength. However, the buff will temporarily deactivate if the companion is incapacitated."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Reinforced Bond",
                  "pageId": 1581002,
                  "revisionId": 2742091,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Alternatively, as reloading restores up to 150 shields, maintaining companion’s shields (including Overshield) over 1200 will activate the buff. Note that Battery Weapons won’t restore shields."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
