                  "pageTitle": "Reinforced Bond",
                  "pageId": 1581002,
                  "revisionId": 2742091,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "In order to get at least 1200 maximum shields with the Calculated Redirection mod at maximum rank, your companion will need a minimum 343 base shield. This can only be accomplished by the following companions:"
