                  "pageId": 1581002,
                  "revisionId": 2742091,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Using a max-rank Link Redirection to reach the required 1200 maximum shields on beast companions is heavily dependent on your selected Warframe's maximum shields. Because different beasts have differing shield values, this can range from needing at least 568 maximum shields on your Warframe for Huras Kubrow to needing at least 776 maximum shields on your Warframe for Adarza Kavat and Smeeta Kavat ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Reinforced Bond",
                  "pageId": 1581002,
                  "revisionId": 2742091,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "For Khora specifically, she will need at least 960 maximum shields on herself to reach at least 1200 shields on Venari , who has 0 base shields."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Reinforced Bond",
                  "pageId": 1581002,
                  "revisionId": 2742091,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Weapons that reload per shell, such as the Strun , will generate Overshields for each shell loaded in."
                }
              },
              {
