                  "revisionId": 2742091,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "As long as a Vulpaphyla 's beast form reaches the 1200 shield threshold, the fire rate buff stays activated in their larval forms, even though the larvae don't have enough shields."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
